---
const appUrl = 'https://app.dwellhub.in';
---

<section class="relative px-8 py-20 lg:py-32 max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
  <div class="lg:col-span-6 z-10">
    <span class="inline-block text-on-tertiary-container bg-tertiary-container/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 font-label">The Modern Curator</span>

    <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-primary tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-4 font-headline">
      Community management, <span class="text-on-tertiary-container italic">made clearer.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-label font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-8">For Apartments, Villas & Gated Communities</p>

    <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed font-body">
      From billing and collections to complaints and compliance, Dwell Hub gives your committee one clear operating system for the whole society. Manage a 50-flat community for just ₹1,000/month with core tools included.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-10">
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl px-5 py-4 min-w-[13rem] editorial-shadow">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant font-label mb-2">Typical Society</p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-primary font-headline">50 flats</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Just ₹1,000/month for billing, complaints, gate, reports, and more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl px-5 py-4 min-w-[13rem] editorial-shadow">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant font-label mb-2">Free Start</p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-primary font-headline">Up to 5 flats</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Start at ₹0, set up quickly, and upgrade only when your society grows.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href={`${appUrl}/register`} class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold tracking-wide hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity editorial-shadow">
        Get Started
      </a>
      <a href="#pricing" class="bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold tracking-wide hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        See Pricing
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lg:col-span-6 relative flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-tertiary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg">
      <dotlottie-player
        src="https://assets-v2.lottiefiles.com/a/358e0c5e-1176-11ee-8663-8f76e1809294/JmwXG8XzU7.lottie"
        background="transparent"
        speed="1"
        style="width: 100%; height: auto;"
        loop
        autoplay
      ></dotlottie-player>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
